data.description: GOLF MEMBERSHIP is included!  You get to enjoy all of amenity rich Bonita National as an owner of this fabulous 4th floor condominium offering gorgeous sunset views over the golf course and lake from your beautiful, screened lanai. Quality throughout with volume ceilings, crown molding, tile on the diagonal, breakfast room, great room design with split bedrooms for maximum comfort. Yours to enjoy - 18 challenging holes of golf, aqua range and putting green, lighted tennis courts and full-service pro shop so you can master your games! For fun in the sun, you are close to the satellite pool for relaxing afternoons or over to the main club where the lagoon style pool with waterfall and lap lanes, pool side cabanas and bar/grill await you and your guests! Thers a full-service salon for pampering and a state-of-the-art fitness center complete w sauna! The main clubhouse is stunning and offers a more formal dining fare, meeting and game rooms, locker rooms and more. Centrally located to sandy gulf beaches, downtown Naples, RSW or the River district in Fort Myers! Loads of shopping and dining destinations are close by and you will appreciate the arts and fun activities offered in SWFL!
